.container
  .marketing 
    .row
      .col-lg-4
        %h2  Make money fast
        %p We make it easy for you to earn extra cash by doing what you do well, selling stuff online.
      / /.col-lg-4
      .col-lg-4
        %h2 No more searching
        %p We connect you to a database of things people want sold for them. You simply sell the item in the marketplace of your choice.
      / /.col-lg-4
      .col-lg-4
        %h2 No hassle shipping
        %p The owner of the item ships directly to the buyer. One less thing for you to worry about.
       
      / /.col-lg-4
