    / START THE FEATURETTES
    %hr.featurette-divider
      %h2.featurette-heading{:style => "margin-bottom: 100px; text-align: center;"} How it works:
      .row.featurette
        .col-md-7{:style => "vertical-align:center;"}
          %h2.featurette-heading
            Step 1
            %span.text-muted Choose an item and make an offer.
          %p.lead Choose an item you know you can sell and make a Vendi-bid. Your Vendi-bid is the amount the owner expects to make once the item sells. If your Vendi-bid is accepted, you are free to sell the item however you want.
        .col-md-5
          %img.featurette-image.img-responsive.center-block{:alt => "Generic placeholder image", src:image_path("grey.png"), :style => "width: 300px;"}
      %hr.featurette-divider
        .row.featurette
          .col-md-5
            %img.featurette-image.img-responsive.center-block{:alt => "Generic placeholder image", src:image_path("grey.png"), :style => "width: 300px;"}
          .col-md-7
            %h2.featurette-heading
              Step 2
              %span.text-muted Find a buyer.
            %p.lead Sell the item for any amount greater than your Vendi-bid. Once you sell the item, send us the Vendi-bid amount, and the item gets shipped to the buyer.
        %hr.featurette-divider
          .row.featurette
            .col-md-7
              %h2.featurette-heading
                Step 3
                %span.text-muted Get paid.
              %p.lead The marketplace you sell the item on pays you directly. You keep the difference between your Vendi-bid and the final selling price!

            .col-md-5
              %img.featurette-image.img-responsive.center-block{:alt => "Generic placeholder image",src:image_path("grey.png"), :style => "width: 300px;"}
